   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="uoedh_hl_h.1543_1.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <dateline>
                  <date when="1925-03-08">March 8</date>
               </dateline>
               <date>
                  <note hand="unknown" rend="pencil">1925</note>
               </date>
               <salute>Dear Mr Hardy</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>I thank you very sincerely for sending "<ref target="#bib:Hardy1887_Woodlanders">The
                  Wood­landers</ref>" for my birthday, it is useless for me to try to tell you how
               much I shall always value my three beautiful books.</p>

            <pb n="2" facs="uoedh_hl_h.1543_2.jpg"/>

            <pb n="3" facs="uoedh_hl_h.1543_3.jpg"/>

            <p>I am so very glad too to know that you are not annoyed with me about the Haymarket
               Matineés</p>

            <closer>
               <salute>Yours sincerely</salute>
               <signed>Gertrude Bugler</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb n="4" facs="uoedh_hl_h.1543_4.jpg"/>

            <idno n="H.1543">H.1543</idno>


         </div>
